"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"bližnjice…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change the way the game looks?"
msgstr "Ali lahko spremenim videz igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, click on the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &kmines;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Da, kliknite na menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmines;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is there a way to add more mines and squares?"
msgstr "Ali obstaja način za dodajanje več min in kvadratov?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, the easiest way is to use the drop down box in the lower right corner."
msgstr "Da, najlažji način je uporaba spustnega menija v spodnjem desnem kotu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game settings can be configured by selecting the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kmines;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. A dialog will appear."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve igre lahko konfigurirate z izbiro menijske postavke "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmines;…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikaže se pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>General</guilabel> page, you can configure the following "
"game settings."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> lahko konfigurirate naslednje "
"nastavitve igre."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use '?' marks"
msgstr "Uporaba '?' oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked, allows using the question mark symbol to mark the squares of "
"uncertainty. The mark on the square can be switched by clicking with &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, dovoljuje uporabo simbola vprašaja za označevanje kvadratov "
"negotovosti. Oznako na kvadratku lahko zamenjate s klikom z &RMB;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow &kmines; reset"
msgstr "Dovoli ponastaviti &kmines;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked, allows you to reset &kmines; game when it is impossible to do "
"anything but guess and your last guess is wrong."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, vam omogoča ponastavitev &kmines; igre, ko je nemogoče "
"storiti karkoli drugega kot ugibati in je vaše zadnje ugibanje napačno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable score on reset"
msgstr "Onemogoči rezultat ob ponastavitvi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "When checked, allows you to disable scoring on reset."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, vam dovoljuje, da onemogočite točkovanje ob ponastavitvi."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Explore with left click on number cells"
msgstr "Raziščite z levim klikom številske celice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked, the &LMB; click on a number cell will have the same effect as "
"the &MMB; click."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, &LMB; klik na številsko celico bo imel enak učinek kot klik "
"na &MMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the second page, you can set the theme. Select a theme from the list. "
"Each item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A "
"selection is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"Na drugi strani lahko nastavite temo. Izberite temo s seznama. Vsak element "
"na seznamu prikazuje majhen predogled levo od imena teme. Izbor se takoj "
"uporabi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the third page, you can set the height and width of the board and the "
"number of mines in your custom level."
msgstr ""
"Na tretji strani lahko nastavite višino in širino plošče ter število min na "
"ravni po meri."

